From 8e29cd9802d902559ab72afc0f7f42c44ecb7484 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hariharan Ramanathan <hramanat@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 26 Sep 2025 17:01:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k: Check for valid peer link before
 processing telemetry peer stats request

When telemetry peer stats are requested for a non-associated link, dummy
stats are currently returned, which is incorrect.

Add a check to ensure the requested link is a valid peer link before
returning stats.

Fixes: I9f3509245c832be4e669944679e9ab8cabf866df
Patch-Dependency:
0429-0001-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Support-for-stats-interface-.patch

Signed-off-by: Hariharan Ramanathan <hramanat@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp.c | 7 +++++++
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp.c
index 6068bbc..a4b71e1 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp.c
@@ -2678,6 +2678,13 @@ int ath12k_dp_get_peer_stats(struct ath12k_vif *ahvif,
 			return -EINVAL;
 		}
 
+		/* Error case handling for non-associated links */
+		if (valid_link && !(peer->peer_links_map & BIT(link_id))) {
+			spin_unlock_bh(&dp_hw->peer_lock);
+			ath12k_err(NULL, "Error MLO peer with invalid link id");
+			return -EINVAL;
+		}
+
 		/*Peer stats of MLD peer for requested link id*/
 		if (valid_link) {
 			rcu_read_lock();
-- 
